

# 🗄️ Database Schema (Screen View)

---

## 👤 Users

| Column Name | Data Type     | Key    | Description           |
| ----------- | ------------- | ------ | --------------------- |
| USERID      | INT           | PK     | Primary Key           |
| FULLNAME    | NVARCHAR(100) |        | Customer Name         |
| EMAIL       | NVARCHAR(100) | UNIQUE | No duplicates allowed |
| PHONENAME   | NVARCHAR(11)  |        | Phone Number          |
| CREATEAT    | DATETIME      |        | Default: Current Date |

---

## 📍 Addresses

| Column Name | Data Type     | Key | Description                   |
| ----------- | ------------- | --- | ----------------------------- |
| ADDRESSESID | INT           | PK  | Primary Key                   |
| USERID      | INT           | FK  | Links to Users                |
| ADDRESSLINE | NVARCHAR(255) |     | Full Address                  |
| CITY        | NVARCHAR(100) |     | Multiple users can share city |
| STATE       | NVARCHAR(100) |     | State                         |
| PINCODE     | NVARCHAR(10)  |     | Postal Code                   |
| CREATEDAT   | DATETIME      |     | Default: Current Date         |

---

## 🏪 Vendors

| Column Name | Data Type     | Key | Description           |
| ----------- | ------------- | --- | --------------------- |
| VENDORID    | INT           | PK  | Primary Key           |
| VENDORNAME  | NVARCHAR(255) |     | Vendor Name           |
| CONTACTMAIL | NVARCHAR(100) |     | Email                 |
| CREATEDAT   | DATETIME      |     | Default: Current Date |

---

## 📂 ProductCategories

| Column Name    | Data Type     | Key | Description |
| -------------- | ------------- | --- | ----------- |
| CATEGORIESID   | INT           | PK  | Primary Key |
| CATEGORIESNAME | NVARCHAR(100) |     | Not Null    |

---

## 📦 Products

| Column Name  | Data Type     | Key | Description           |
| ------------ | ------------- | --- | --------------------- |
| PRODUCTSID   | INT           | PK  | Identity(1,1)         |
| PRODUCTSNAME | NVARCHAR(100) |     | Not Null              |
| DESCRIPTION  | NVARCHAR(255) |     | Product Description   |
| CATEGORIESID | INT           | FK  | Links to Categories   |
| PRICE        | DECIMAL(10,2) |     | Product Price         |
| CREATEDAT    | DATETIME      |     | Default: Current Date |

---

## 📊 Inventory

| Column Name       | Data Type | Key | Description           |
| ----------------- | --------- | --- | --------------------- |
| INVENTORYID       | INT       | PK  | Primary Key           |
| VENDORID          | INT       | FK  | Links to Vendors      |
| PRODUCTSID        | INT       | FK  | Links to Products     |
| QUANTITYAVAILABLE | INT       |     | Stock Level           |
| LASTUPDATED       | DATETIME  |     | Default: Current Date |

---

## 🧾 Orders

| Column Name | Data Type     | Key | Description           |
| ----------- | ------------- | --- | --------------------- |
| ORDERSID    | INT           | PK  | Identity(1,1)         |
| VENDORID    | INT           | FK  | Links to Vendors      |
| USERID      | INT           | FK  | Links to Users        |
| ORDERUPDATE | DATETIME      |     | Default: Current Date |
| TOTALAMOUNT | DECIMAL(10,2) |     | Total Amount          |

---

## 🛒 OrdersItem

| Column Name  | Data Type     | Key | Description         |
| ------------ | ------------- | --- | ------------------- |
| ORDERSITEMID | INT           | PK  | Primary Key         |
| ORDERSID     | INT           | FK  | Links to Orders     |
| PRODUCTSID   | INT           | FK  | Links to Products   |
| QUANTITY     | INT           |     | Quantity            |
| PRICE        | DECIMAL(10,2) |     | Price at Order Time |

---

## 💳 Payments

| Column Name   | Data Type    | Key | Description           |
| ------------- | ------------ | --- | --------------------- |
| PAYMENTID     | INT          | PK  | Primary Key           |
| ORDERSID      | INT          | FK  | Links to Orders       |
| PAYMENTMODE   | NVARCHAR(50) |     | Cash/Card/UPI         |
| PAYMENTSTATUS | NVARCHAR(50) |     | Pending/Paid/Failed   |
| PAIDAT        | DATETIME     |     | Default: Current Date |

---

## 🚚 DeliveryPayments

| Column Name   | Data Type    | Key | Description  |
| ------------- | ------------ | --- | ------------ |
| PARTNERID     | INT          | PK  | Primary Key  |
| FULLNAME      | NVARCHAR(50) |     | Partner Name |
| PAYMENTSTATUS | NVARCHAR(11) |     | Status       |

---

## 📌 Status

| Column Name | Data Type    | Key | Description    |
| ----------- | ------------ | --- | -------------- |
| STATUSID    | INT          | PK  | Primary Key    |
| STATUSNAME  | NVARCHAR(50) |     | e.g. Delivered |

---

## 🚀 DeliveryStatus

| Column Name | Data Type | Key | Description           |
| ----------- | --------- | --- | --------------------- |
| DELIVERYID  | INT       | PK  | Primary Key           |
| ORDERSID    | INT       | FK  | Links to Orders       |
| STATUSID    | INT       | FK  | Links to Status       |
| UPDATEDAT   | DATETIME  |     | Default: Current Date |

---

## ⭐ Reviews

| Column Name | Data Type     | Key | Description           |
| ----------- | ------------- | --- | --------------------- |
| REVIEWSID   | INT           | PK  | Primary Key           |
| USERID      | INT           | FK  | Links to Users        |
| PRODUCTSID  | INT           | FK  | Links to Products     |
| RATING      | INT           |     | 1–5                   |
| COMMENT     | NVARCHAR(150) |     | Review Text           |
| CREATEDAT   | DATETIME      |     | Default: Current Date |

---


